PrecisOrder directing that a PROCLAMATION do issue giving notice that (a) the PROTOCOL to the CONVENTION between CANADA and the REPUBLIC OF INDONESIA for the AVOIDANCE OF DOUBLE TAXATION and the PREVENTION OF FISCAL EVASION with respect to TAXES ON INCOME and on CAPITAL, signed on April 1, 1998, came into force on December 31, 1998, and (b) the Protocol signed at Jakarta on January 16, 1979, ceases to have effect in respect of a taxable period beginning on or after January 1, 1999.
RegistrationRegistration: SI / 1999-0077 Publication Date: 1999-07-21
Attachments
precis:
Order directing that a PROCLAMATION do issue giving notice that (a) the
PROTOCOL to the CONVENTION between CANADA and the REPUBLIC OF INDONESIA for
the AVOIDANCE OF DOUBLE TAXATION and the PREVENTION OF FISCAL EVASION with
respect to TAXES ON INCOME and on CAPITAL, signed on April 1, 1998, came
into force on December 31, 1998, and (b) the Protocol signed at Jakarta on
January 16, 1979, ceases to have effect in respect of a taxable period
beginning on or after January 1, 1999.
